澎湃新闻记者 张伟龙2月18日，仙桃市卫健委的一份通知引发热议，通知包括严禁群内讨论疫情、擅自接受采访等内容。
Peng Pai journalist Zhang Weilong February 18, Xiantao Health Committee of a notice triggered hot discussion, including a ban on group discussion of the epidemic, unauthorized interviews and other content.
Play澎湃新闻记者 张伟龙 编辑 杨丹 视频来源 相关人士责任编辑：周宽玮校对：刘威19日晚，仙桃卫健委回应澎湃新闻称通知内容属实。
Zhang Weilong journalist Zhang Weilong editing Yang Dan responsible editor: Zhou Guanwei proofread: Liu Wei on the night of 19, Xiantao Wei health committee in response to the roar news that the notice is true.
相关人员介绍由于在前期防疫工作中，该市卫生健康系统个别人员出现泄露确诊患者个人信息、传播未经证实的疫情信息等情况，对患者及其家属和全市疫情防控工作带来一定影响。
Relevant personnel introduced that in the pre-epidemic work, the city's health and health system individual personnel leaked the confirmed patient's personal information, spread the unconfirmed epidemic information, and so on, to the patients, their families and the city-wide epidemic prevention and control work.
为严肃工作纪律，严格规范文件传送和信息发布渠道，仙桃市卫生健康委于2月18日晚出台了该《通知》。
The notice was issued on the night of February 18 by the Sanitary and Health Commission of the city of Xiantao to strictly regulate file transfer and information distribution channels for serious work discipline.
针对网民讨论，该工作人员表示，下发《通知》的初衷并非是对疫情信息进行封锁，也不是拒绝媒体采访报道，但“相关文字表述确有不当之处”。
In response to a discussion among Internet users, the official said the notice was not intended to block epidemic information or deny access to the media, but "there is something wrong with the wording."
▲仙桃市卫健委发出的《关于重申疫情防控期间有关纪律的通知》引发舆论关注。
Xiantao Health Committee issued the "Reaffirming the disease during the relevant disciplinary notice" aroused public concern.
图片来自网络目前，仙桃市卫生健康委已于当日召开紧急会议，要求全市卫健系统干部职工切实改进工作方式方法，检视存在的问题和不足，以更加严谨的态度、更加务实的作风，做好疫情防控工作。
At present, the Xiantao Health Committee has held an emergency meeting on the same day, asking cadres and staff of the city's health care system to improve ways and means of work, examine the existing problems and shortcomings, with a more rigorous attitude, a more pragmatic style of work, to do a good job of disease prevention and control.
